low-power caveat: 1036 symbols, 1027 transitions, and 6889 cells in an 83x83 matrix (mean 0.149 transitions/cell; 12.48 symbols/value). An inside-shuffle row is only a null-comparison result at this corpus size, not proof of memorylessness.
entropy correction: add-constant alpha=1.0 over the full 83-symbol next-state support; raw plug-in MI is shown only as a sparse-sample diagnostic

